cs.CV, cs.IT, cs.MM, cs.OH, cs.NE 

This paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it presents a new color image reconstruction algorithm for a single-photon detector. Additionally, information theory (cs.IT) and multimedia (cs.MM) sub-categories are also likely as the paper discusses the use of truncated Poisson statistics and variance stabilizing transforms in the algorithm. The paper may also belong to the other computer science (cs.OH) sub-category as it presents a new sensor design. Finally, the neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE) sub-category is also possible as the paper discusses the use of machine learning techniques in the algorithm.
